children.name: Rules
children.text: Once per day, while taking a Short Rest, the target can eat some food from this replenishing sack lunch. It only replenishes enough for 1 person per Long Rest. If not eaten within an hour, the food instantly begins to rot. Treat one of the hit dice rolled for this short rest as having rolled the maximum number. The eater also regains one first level spell slot during this short rest, and has advantage on their next constitution saving throw made before their next Long Rest.
